         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">Journalist and war correspondent. Papers consist of correspondence, writings, biographical material, photographs and memorabilia.  Includes letters home during World War II; her coverage of the Nuremburg trials and the United Nations European Headquarters in Geneva; and her letters and journal from Brazzaville, French Equatorial Africa.  Also included are unpublished stories, radio broadcasts, two scrapbooks and letters to her father.
